{"tid":454161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寶蓮寺長老與尼姑「曖昧」同遊夏威夷","createTime":"2017-11-01T01:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T08:57:55.000Z","uid":130816,"like":224,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"76fa9d3e168e7f6d44a1e0a2f4d2ea98eba13bf2","tid":454161,"uid":130816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:03:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AF%B6%E8%93%AE%E5%AF%BA%E9%95%B7%E8%80%81%E8%88%87%E5%B0%BC%E5%A7%91-%E6%9B%96%E6%98%A7-%E5%90%8C%E9%81%8A%E5%A4%8F%E5%A8%81%E5%A4%B7-221112305.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E8%2593%25AE%25E5%25AF%25BA%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2581%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E5%25A7%2591-%25E6%259B%2596%25E6%2598%25A7-%25E5%2590%258C%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25A4%258F%25E5%25A8%2581%25E5%25A4%25B7-221112305.html&d=r%2B%2FiB006GaAC7ImnPZ1Qyb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=f8615472\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AF%B6%E8%93%AE%E5%AF%BA%E9%95%B7%E8%80%81%E8%88%87%E5%B0%BC%E5%A7%91-%E6%9B%96%E6%98%A7-%E5%90%8C%E9%81%8A%E5%A4%8F%E5%A8%81%E5%A4%B7-221112305.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/090251_a254f1484a43d14ac7280934cf2d4dff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F090251_a254f1484a43d14ac7280934cf2d4dff.jpg&h=b801deee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】繼《頭條日報》早前揭露仁慈寺方丈涉性侵女善信而被捕後，佛門又爆醜聞。《頭條日報》記者採訪發現，世界聞名的大嶼山寶蓮寺長老與尼姑，被揭關係「曖昧」，涉嚴重違反戒律。本報取得一名匿名善信所提供的美國私家偵探調查報告，當中大量相片顯示寶蓮寺首座（資深大和尚）釋健釗，今年五月與女弟子心慧法師結伴遊夏威夷，二人入住由寶蓮寺斥資購買的獨立大屋，共處數天，出雙入對，又租車遊玩，出入五星級酒店、於露天海灘餐廳共進自助餐，女方更穿「三點式」泳衣露出臀部，臥在沙灘椅上日光浴，雙方貌甚親熱，恍如情侶。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，位於夏威夷莫基哈納聖三千六百多方呎兩層高連車房大屋，業主為寶蓮寺(夏威夷）佛教會，於〇九年以一百二十八萬美元購入，名「寶蓮禪寺（夏威夷）佛教會舍」，大廳設佛壇，但鮮有信眾入內供奉，屋內有多間睡房，全設雙人牀鋪，浴室有雙人按摩缸。現年七十歲的釋健釗與五十四歲的心慧每年夏天都結伴往夏威夷，入住獨立屋度假數周。二人抵埗後會先租車，由心慧駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n本報取得一份美國私家偵探調查報告，大量相片顯示心慧與釋健釗出入獨立屋時，必戴上鴨舌帽及黑超。心慧駕駛期間，周圍張望，似恐被人目睹，她又常超速駕駛。消息稱，五月二十八日早上九時半兩人着便裝、戴上鴨舌帽及黑超，登上紅色房車，駛往五星級酒店Kahala（凱海蘭度假村酒店），該酒店為當地最豪華的沙灘酒店，不少皇室、明星、富豪，以及元首曾下榻。心慧及釋健釗抵達後，心慧從車上取毛巾，偕釋健釗步出酒店露天餐廳，二人似一早訂了望海雅座，並肩而坐，一邊吃自助餐一邊說笑，不時「咬耳仔」，表現輕鬆，有時開懷大笑。<br />\n<br />\n約兩小時後，大約中午，心慧脫去Ｔ恤及長褲，僅穿深藍色圓點「三點式」泳衣，在沙灘曬太陽，露出臀部，她有時脫去帽子，手抓抓短髮，不一會又戴上，釋健釗站在附近樹蔭下望着她。十多分鐘後，釋健釗拿手機致電心慧，心慧接電後穿回Ｔ恤，二人匯合，一起行至魚池觀賞，心慧把手搭在健釗膊上。未幾心慧把停車證交給酒店員工，二人登上紅色房車，由心慧駕車返回佛舍。<br />\n<br />\n據知，二人返抵佛舍後，一直沒外出。鄰居說，這對男女過去十年來每年都到獨立屋旅居數星期，每次二人都穿便服、戴鴨舌帽及黑超，甚少有其他人到訪，每晚都聽見一些男女聲浪從屋內浴室傳出。"},{"pid":"dfcfa8e0e6738895b03b404af5eca25d6b5f5880","tid":454161,"uid":47674,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:08:49.000Z","msg":"花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c0ce52fbba15005d5be5acd810ee1b0962db9a","tid":454161,"uid":20317,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:09:41.000Z","msg":"真係我佛慈悲"},{"pid":"9d130dd9abfbf5e68e1aece39e6967bfd58bf007","tid":454161,"uid":22858,"like":79,"dislike":7,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:10:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">召喚翁靜晶</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><ins>細字濃縮試用版</ins><br />\n經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據一：五毛一見字眼空群而出</ins><br />\n連狗對五毛問題視而不見、置若罔聞，與全連登作對<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451623\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451623</a><br />\n【枕戈待旦】有關被連狗封鎖禁言之嚴正聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/442843\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/442843</a><br />\n刺刀捅向習匪頭 鏟平地獄鬼國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/439819\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/439819</a><br />\n【黑暗】濕鳩塞鷗兄已遭連尼住禁言七日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/435231\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/435231</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據二：五毛擾亂視聽妖言惑眾</ins><br />\nJR：(人手置頂) 屈毛黨名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/405731\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/405731</a><br />\nRedBaron：關愛座呢隻五毛都算高招<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451674\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451674</a><br />\nGladiclus：（大踢爆）關愛座hunter係5毛！被bam屈毛派親身指證！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451720\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451720</a><br />\nJR：要求admin立即ban左三位會員︰關愛座hunter, 濕鳩塞鷗, 1000歲人瑞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451747\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451747</a><br />\nRedBaron（已改名）：香港獨立之後一定要實行獨裁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/452801\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/452801</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9fb8e1451c6cb03348b9efe636a9abb23e79fee3","tid":454161,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:11:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57d4555e04978f305cc67085e1f2ff96d040b125","tid":454161,"uid":72058,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:12:44.000Z","msg":"淫僧有（慾）火<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f213c1c30ab0499e58ba46e326744a98925a04","tid":454161,"uid":895,"like":135,"dislike":1,"score":134,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:12:55.000Z","msg":"每晚都聽見一些男女聲浪從屋內浴室傳出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n念緊佛經jei<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3215cf3b2403615b28bc5f521b6ed0fd899dffb","tid":454161,"uid":22535,"like":258,"dislike":0,"score":258,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:15:20.000Z","msg":"長老每晚對尼姑講，我佛你，我佛你"},{"pid":"5e74c72a9abdd22008ed1543bedc3cf2b0687259","tid":454161,"uid":135313,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:15:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b01f86847648672288f93dbf1b59c1d37307d66","tid":454161,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:16:45.000Z","msg":"呢d叫入世歷練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08691990f74db2bcd11d7900ed343feddc036c40","tid":454161,"uid":47674,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:16:53.000Z","msg":"色即是胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e89ceb9ae79cddb64cedeeafb42164b7e72f43","tid":454161,"uid":6297,"like":2,"dislike":30,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:17:47.000Z","msg":"咁都有得屈"},{"pid":"25152111c533bbe120ab6c90e065713ecba1d25e","tid":454161,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:18:02.000Z","msg":"唔知間酒店自助餐啲燒牛肉好唔好食呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0392e601ee8f65cea69c541656660e109eacae28","tid":454161,"uid":34410,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:18:23.000Z","msg":"佛撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d7dd4ef4817406718311200c9ea01fe8bf1bf7","tid":454161,"uid":46454,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:19:19.000Z","msg":"佛門向來都唔係清淨地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3f993f0aa5e95ee3ab352e8b3b4f689e46d61c","tid":454161,"uid":63670,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:19:54.000Z","msg":"戒左70年依家屌下都唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0821cd7e017f4b929dcacda7047ccb25c8068b36","tid":454161,"uid":47674,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:20:01.000Z","msg":"釋健釗後台雄厚 經常到內地弘法<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1690236&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1690236%26target%3D2&d=r%2B%2FiB006GaAC7ImnPZ1Qyb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=18e14620\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1690236%26target%3D2&h=e5e3ebcd\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1690236&amp;target=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2017/11/01/301416/i_343x255_082215716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F301416%2Fi_343x255_082215716.jpg&h=40cab3c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寶蓮寺長老釋健釗與女弟子心慧法師，被揭關係「曖昧」。<br />\n<br />\n(星島日報報道)釋健釗法師，廣東中山人，現任澳門佛教總會會長，世界佛教僧伽會副會長，澳門菩提禪院住持，荃灣南天竺寺住持，寶蓮禪寺座元和尚兼都監。<br />\n<br />\n　　一九六〇年，健釗於澳門智心佛堂依智圓長老出家，六三年赴香港寶蓮禪寺依筏可大和尚受戒，及後駐錫本港，弘法事業，八七年法師在丹霞山別傳寺接本煥長老法脈，至九四年出任澳門菩提禪院住持，九六年倡議成立「澳門佛教總會」，積極推動澳門佛教的發展，增加佛教在社會上的正面影響力，翌年創辦《澳門佛教》刊物及每年於菩提禪院舉辦靜修營，藉以讓社會大眾易於接觸和了解佛教知識。<br />\n<br />\n　　健釗亦是香港佛聯會會長釋覺光弟子，後台實力雄厚，〇九年起健釗與國家宗教局官員交往密切，經常到內地弘法。寶蓮寺於早年開始舉辦的「佛你跑」，都是健釗聯同心慧法師推廣恆常運動的概念，通過接觸不同熱愛跑步人士，雙方增進了解，尤其一般人總覺得法師是高高在上，遇到有事也不敢請教。<br />\n<br />\n　　心慧法師原籍是廣東省順德人，一九六三年出生於香港。自幼在佛教家庭中長大，所以順理成章，小學、中學都在佛教學校就讀。就讀中學期間，修讀佛學專修班三年。跟隨源慧、寬如、寬如法師學經，其後研讀楞嚴經講習班兩年。八七年五月取得文學學士學位。同年六月禮上覺下能法師出家。秋期在大嶼山寶蓮禪寺，求受三壇大戒後於藏經樓，閱讀藏經三年，主管藏經樓事務和寶蓮禪寺秘書。<br />\n<br />\n　　寶蓮禪寺天壇大佛開光後二年，就隨健釗長老轉到澳門菩提禪院，服務常住，來澳後出版澳門佛教雜誌兩年，澳門佛教總會成立後，就一直擔任主編，每期以不同筆名發表文章。於香港每年經常往佛教中學為學生作專題性的佛學講座。曾應邀到澳門普濟蓮峰學校，每星期為小四至小六的學生主講佛學四年。每年澳門菩提之旅靜修營擔任講師或導師之職。代表澳門出席世界佛教論壇並發表論文。"},{"pid":"3fb33246fbd3d78e3108789288310e4b23502001","tid":454161,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"670e8711911f0a9996c13244bd030763107c6031","tid":454161,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:21:50.000Z","msg":"釋健釗後台厚　收心慧為弟子<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/616685/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F616685%2F&d=r%2B%2FiB006GaAC7ImnPZ1Qyb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=bb906eee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F616685%2F&h=9ac57435\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/616685/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2017/11/01/301565/i_640x477_086418643.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F301565%2Fi_640x477_086418643.jpg&h=3762c51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獨立屋內有多間房間，均設雙人牀鋪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2017/11/01/301565/i_640x478_030413365.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F301565%2Fi_640x478_030413365.jpg&h=cabae13d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩人入住寶蓮寺在當地購入的獨立屋。<br />\n<br />\n釋健釗與心慧屬師徒關係，在寶蓮寺天壇大佛開光後二年，心慧隨釋健釗到澳門菩提憚院，服務常住。<br />\n<br />\n　　釋健釗法師，廣東中山人，現任澳門佛教總會會長、世界佛教僧伽會副會長、澳門菩提禪院住持、荃灣南天竺寺住持、寶蓮禪寺座元和尚兼都監。一九六○年，他於澳門智心佛堂依智圓長老出家，六三年赴香港寶蓮禪寺依筏可大和尚受戒，八七年法師在丹霞山別傳寺接本煥長老法脈，至九四年出任澳門菩提禪院住持，九六年倡議成立「澳門佛教總會」，推動澳門佛教的發展，增加佛教在社會上的正面影響力，翌年創辦《澳門佛教》刊物及每年於菩提禪院舉辦靜修營，藉以讓社會大眾易於接觸和了解佛教知識。<br />\n<br />\n　　釋健釗亦是香港佛聯會會長釋覺光弟子，後台實力雄厚，○九年起他與國家宗教局官員交往密切，經常到內地弘法。寶蓮寺於早年開始舉辦的「佛你跑」，都是釋健釗聯同心慧法師推廣恒常運動的概念。<br />\n<br />\n　　心慧法師原籍是廣東省順德人，六三年出生於香港。自幼在佛教家庭中長大。就讀中學期間，修讀佛學專修班三年。八七年五月取得文學學士學位。同年六月禮上覺下能法師出家。秋期在大嶼山寶蓮禪寺，求受三壇大戒後於藏經樓，閱讀藏經三年，主管藏經樓事務和寶蓮禪寺秘書。"},{"pid":"9cd7a391ccd4e8e8e3a135e8d3b8ee69e81a71db","tid":454161,"uid":47674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:23:22.000Z","msg":"僧尼外遊共處一室酒店食大餐「六根不清淨」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/616688/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F616688%2F&d=r%2B%2FiB006GaAC7ImnPZ1Qyb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=b858c016\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F616688%2F&h=6255b084\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/616688/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佛家追求四大皆空，六根清淨，和尚尼姑須遵從森嚴戒律。身為寶蓮寺首座長老的釋健釗法師與女弟子兼寶蓮寺秘書心慧法師，竟多次結伴遠赴夏威夷度假，孤男寡女共住一屋，同吃同行，朝夕相對，每早一起駕車外出，於星級酒店享用豪華午餐及曬日光浴，完全與佛教戒律背道而馳。記者︰徐曉伊<br />\n<br />\n        從匿名善信所提供的私家偵探拍得的影片所見，心慧穿比堅尼泳衣，塗上太陽油，臥在沙灘椅上享受日光浴，根據佛教規條，出家和尚及尼姑不得游泳，不准單獨同處一室及過夜，不准同食，不可穿著便裝出外，但健釗和心慧不但一起外遊，更二人共處一屋，心慧更穿三點式，露出臀部，搭着師傅健釗的脖子同行，有講有笑，儼如一對情侶般。<br />\n<br />\n房車「SUM WAI」作車牌<br />\n<br />\n　　出家人應「六根清淨」，根據匿名善信提供由美國私家偵探拍得的照片，心慧房間內有大量的宮廷鬥連續劇和小說，例如《還珠格格》、《風雲再起》、《悲喜重重》、《陰差陽錯》以及《紅塵作伴》等。於六三年出生的心慧更以平治房車代步，名下房車以她的法號英文譯音「SUM WAI」作車牌。出家人若貪圖五欲享受就是墮落，沒有資格被叫做僧人或尼姑。<br />\n<br />\n　　消息指，自幼喪雙親的釋健釗法師，幸遇上一位寺院住持引導他入佛門，學習佛學，健釗成為兩間寺廟的住持後，寺廟專收容那些無依無靠的可憐人，這些人幾十年來都不會被趕出寺廟，都將寺廟當作家。由於小時候沒有機會讀書的健釗法師，最敬佩受過良好教育的人，他希望年輕一輩的出家人有學識，故慷慨地資助他們讀學士及碩士，甚至博士。<br />\n<br />\n　　心慧是健釗身邊關係非同一般的女徒弟，她也是寶蓮寺的尼僧兼高層人員。健釗任澳門佛教總會會長，心慧便是澳門佛教總會副會長；健釗任香港南天竺寺住持，心慧便是香港南天竺寺監院；健釗任澳門菩提禪院住持，心慧便是澳門菩提禪院理事長；健釗任菩提社會服務委員會主席，心慧便是菩提社會服務委員會副主席；健釗任世界佛教僧伽會副會長，心慧便是世界佛教僧伽會福利委員；健釗任香港寶蓮禪寺董事兼都監，心慧便是香港寶蓮禪寺秘書長。"},{"pid":"f1d8524a07466824faa41b42d4e2cd3cdd94c79d","tid":454161,"uid":57205,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:23:35.000Z","msg":"佛呢樣野而家已經係一門生意<br />\n真係當佢清靜地就輸了"},{"pid":"67913881c8c208ca509bf0605899191f752cbf47","tid":454161,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:24:33.000Z","msg":"同屬寶蓮寺高層 高僧嗒泳裝尼姑 夏威夷秘密幽會<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/616682/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F616682%2F&d=r%2B%2FiB006GaAC7ImnPZ1Qyb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=91e52fbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F616682%2F&h=28e5a825\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/616682/</a><br />\n<br />\n﻿穿泳衣袒胸露臂犯下大戒<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/616691/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F616691%2F&d=r%2B%2FiB006GaAC7ImnPZ1Qyb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=0cf9f07a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F616691%2F&h=a4190150\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/616691/</a>"},{"pid":"8083df9da652d7caa93c20750a14b1510afd6f45","tid":454161,"uid":55096,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:27:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佛呢樣野而家已經係一門生意<br />\n真係當佢清靜地就輸了</blockquote><br />\n所有宗教都係生意 仲唔洗交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100cbd85b041cb6be4c65ce645aec40765f9dbdb","tid":454161,"uid":82507,"like":15,"dislike":12,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佛呢樣野而家已經係一門生意<br />\n真係當佢清靜地就輸了</blockquote><br />\n所有宗教都係生意 仲唔洗交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本佛教就係不事生產<br />\n所謂感化世人，目的都只係為咗自己功德圓滿成佛，好撚虛偽"},{"pid":"dbc79c56998cacb55417937be1c34d9f94f1fc8a","tid":454161,"uid":75993,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:29:54.000Z","msg":"老納？"},{"pid":"5d57eeedb56505878885a74f53153125fd51ade3","tid":454161,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:31:07.000Z","msg":"同大陸接規<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18581301184f424f1ef834fe9ed4247e1a6644a6","tid":454161,"uid":1082,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:31:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每晚都聽見一些男女聲浪從屋內浴室傳出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n念緊佛經jei<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n70 歲 vs 54歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d42846f8a2c526d24d34a6a087ca767ddd10630","tid":454161,"uid":36784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:31:51.000Z","msg":"所謂，我不入地獄，誰入地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f4105741157bfef184ecb9b0d8ff75868026f0","tid":454161,"uid":40272,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:32:15.000Z","msg":"最呃錢就係宗教 <br />\n無本生利 衰撚過走毒"},{"pid":"78756815ec5b74ff48aa2b8f2e5b413ca5ee82b9","tid":454161,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:33:25.000Z","msg":"三點式圖？"},{"pid":"65680573c2caf72e595e88695172050ea0bd138c","tid":454161,"uid":48947,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:34:14.000Z","msg":"香港十之八九都酒肉和尚黎<br />\n食好住好，仲話善信供養<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"ac355556adffde2eb50faf963ec4778670d488cf","tid":454161,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":49,"score":-49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三點式圖？</blockquote><br />\n暫時未見，睇住呢張先<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2017/11/01/301568/i_640x1138_700541656.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F301568%2Fi_640x1138_700541656.jpg&h=83c33893&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7855798112dfeccafa292e88010469b34372ed2","tid":454161,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c8d45f52049536a8b0f142c7559b5e5d373d79","tid":454161,"uid":1082,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:37:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三點式圖？</blockquote><br />\n巴打果然有品味，54歲你都啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adcd6bc89dc27a0b36345e8bc7769e9397777a4","tid":454161,"uid":26089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:37:31.000Z","msg":"不戒和尚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d33322b5bb7b96dbf5d9a965dfc6cf32e258d2","tid":454161,"uid":28163,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:37:33.000Z","msg":"邊個請呢間私家偵探<br />\n未又係等上位既佛門中人<br />\n成班出家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079bf9b88bc1a69a3f091bfd025fc4feafad9fe5","tid":454161,"uid":521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:40:11.000Z","msg":"閉關修練佛門更高境界－歡喜禪"},{"pid":"6bc1aa49b6ca1cfac39d99b356f1cf8e17305e99","tid":454161,"uid":29423,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:42:14.000Z","msg":"帶杜蕾斯的淫僧"},{"pid":"b0b52745bd527f285030c7830dbc41d703f026af","tid":454161,"uid":47359,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:42:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個請呢間私家偵探<br />\n未又係等上位既佛門中人<br />\n成班出家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鬼打鬼唔緊要<br />\n最緊要花生"},{"pid":"fcb22c626a3ab7e6dff59407651ceb80e4d12935","tid":454161,"uid":117837,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:47:13.000Z","msg":"juno隻碟evil is a point of view<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c8a81b225d49a24743e425eae8fc8a38730e98","tid":454161,"uid":132038,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:48:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"856e867ff4e6e205e168f56017ef2d0478abd09c","tid":454161,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:50:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52a6a474fd94744f1f16183fb36b22f9a19569ef","tid":454161,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶杜蕾斯的淫僧</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822c4cd5a19bb9eb4cb378de3e820104c05cfd99","tid":454161,"uid":38651,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"七十歲都有心有力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 晚晚扑嘢<br />\n定還是忍左成年 全部留番度假呢幾日?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd50fae315e43ce25eeacc4ed7f71912e7d927e8","tid":454161,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:12:02.000Z","msg":"不戒和尚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423230cb8bebcf2562adea39d1706620216473b8","tid":454161,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:17:36.000Z","msg":"未食過尼姑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8207d14677bd287661a22591896894d1e44eaa","tid":454161,"uid":37735,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:17:38.000Z","msg":"宗教呢樣野 自古以來都係生意多過個信仰  加入宗教 一半個係撈油水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你對比明清 佛教人數就知  明朝有糧餉同免田租  同 清朝 被人主動打壓<br />\n<br />\n支那古代 一堆人做和尚 只係為逃生，逃避農作  所謂支那幾次要搞滅佛 將一堆和尚變返生產力<br />\n<br />\n淫亂之事 更多不勝數 所謂貴婦人 私通和尚(最出名高陽) 成間佛寺都係淫窟 記載更係多不勝數<br />\n反政府更唔好講 幫政府維穩就有 <br />\n<br />\n少林寺唔乾淨唔係第一日  只不過一直表面扮野  直到共狗釋永信 連表面都唔扮<br />\n搵錢，開課程，搞bba，積極奶共<br />\n<br />\n西方 伊斯蘭教  最後的先知穆罕默得......<br />\n又係講守則，法律最叻<br />\n但自己唔會守<br />\n4個妻子  佢幾十個都來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n不停玩幼女<br />\n聖戰果堆concept 其實都係搵錢多 <br />\n搶哂拜火教等的課金 <br />\n<br />\n耶教 最近有消息話耶教有機會同中共妥協 你唔好奇 個教庭由古至今 都只係依附強權/搵錢至上/有勢力人士 避孕套<br />\n<br />\n先唔講幾多銀<br />\n<br />\n反加獨  美名 反民族主義(心諗 關你撚事)<br />\n又傳奶共<br />\n二戰 希特拉 墨索尼里 所謂嚴守中立<br />\n(加泰又唔見你中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n保碌二世點解會咁出力<br />\n咪又係大老闆歐洲，美國支持<br />\n再諗下蘇聯控制的東正教勢力區 <br />\n一直唔妥"},{"pid":"801c5cdc8833bee22c236bb794673abc88c7aabd","tid":454161,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c33ceaba8e2ec429c9ec66639ea20a3dd46cdc","tid":454161,"uid":3161,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:18:41.000Z","msg":"Dat ass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c043d7ba8d6bb41b4ba3f45e4b1dcb40455ec969","tid":454161,"uid":21917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:19:07.000Z","msg":"會唔會出現呢幕:<br />\n禿驢 你竟敢與貧道搶師太<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56099be4faeeb439df414a8b93bc3283bf4d1eb4","tid":454161,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:20:10.000Z","msg":"修歡喜禪啫"},{"pid":"0952d5fe7efea1f8912e04a37238352b8a17d6a8","tid":454161,"uid":37735,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:21:07.000Z","msg":"宗教呢樣野 自古以來都係生意多過個信仰  加入宗教 一半個係撈油水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你對比明清 佛教人數就知  明朝有糧餉同免田租  同 清朝 被人主動打壓<br />\n<br />\n支那古代 一堆人做和尚 只係為逃稅，逃避農作  所謂支那幾次要搞滅佛 將一堆和尚變返生產力<br />\n<br />\n淫亂之事 更多不勝數 所謂貴婦人 私通和尚(最出名高陽) 成間佛寺都係淫窟 記載更係多不勝數<br />\n反政府更唔好講 幫政府維穩就有 <br />\n<br />\n少林寺唔乾淨唔係第一日  只不過一直表面扮野  直到共狗釋永信 連表面都唔扮<br />\n搵錢，開課程，搞bba，積極奶共<br />\n<br />\n西方 伊斯蘭教  最後的先知穆罕默得......<br />\n又係講守則，法律最叻<br />\n但自己唔會守<br />\n4個妻子  佢幾十個都來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n不停玩幼女<br />\n聖戰果堆concept 其實都係搵錢多 <br />\n搶哂拜火教等的課金 <br />\n<br />\n耶教 最近有消息話耶教有機會同中共妥協 你唔好奇 個教庭由古至今 都只係依附強權/搵錢至上/有勢力人士 避孕套<br />\n<br />\n先唔講幾多銀<br />\n<br />\n先講古代 玩大航海的人 應該知一個叫盧克雷齊亞的人 教主 私生女 <br />\n佢個家族同耶教 長期關係不清<br />\n<br />\n反加獨  美名 反民族主義(心諗 關你撚事)<br />\n又傳奶共<br />\n二戰 希特拉 墨索尼里 所謂嚴守中立<br />\n(加泰又唔見你中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n保碌二世點解會咁出力<br />\n咪又係大老闆歐洲，美國支持<br />\n再諗下蘇聯控制的東正教勢力區 <br />\n一直唔妥"},{"pid":"9627e8bb466b0a99c3c27c6e69242bbbed047c6b","tid":454161,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:23:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>中環出更：方丈換人風波 健釗激動</strong><br />\n2015年11月16日<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20151116/00176_130.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20151116%2F00176_130.html&d=r%2B%2FiB006GaAC7ImnPZ1Qyb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=3fd51ca8\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20151116/00176_130.html</a><br />\n<br />\n寶蓮禪寺尋日舉行第八任方丈淨因陞座典禮，第七任方丈釋智慧正式退下。對於近日紛紛擾擾的佛教界是非，釋智慧只簡單回應「放下」及「我都係睇你哋寫咩」。淨因方丈則指，釋智慧對寶蓮寺的貢獻無法否定，永遠是寶蓮禪寺的長老，至於寺方未來發展大方向將着重文化、教育及淨化心靈上。<br />\n<br />\n儀式完結後，釋健釗長老及淨因方丈接受傳媒訪問，談及未來發展方向，但一提起早前定慧寺主持釋智定假結婚事件，淨因就立即封口，改由經驗豐富的健釗代為應對。健釗面對傳媒尖銳提問時對答如流，又引用例子稱掉一塊磚頭落水時會引起漣漪，但無第二塊磚頭掉落，水面就會慢慢平靜，話傳媒不斷追擊同一個問題等於不斷投石落水，無法靜下，與佛家追求寧靜背道而馳。<br />\n<br />\n「你哋記者多事」<br />\n健釗理解傳媒為何追問，但認為自己無處理社會呢啲複雜問題嘅責任，亦無執法權力，只能靜觀其變，強調事件非傳媒或佛教界能夠解決，只有法律能處理。不過，佢話咁做並非代表放任，至於是否需要整頓佛門，佢話<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>出家人違反戒條就已喪失出家人的資格。</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到點解新方丈唔係之前傳聞接位嘅宏通法師又或佢本人時，原本氣定神閒嘅健釗長老就面色一沉。話說釋智慧嘅方丈之位，本傳聞係健釗繼位，但後來釋智慧改口風，於活動上指宏通法師係「未來方丈」，誰知最後兩人均失落方丈之位，新方丈變成淨因。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當問及此事因由時，健釗長老就話：「如果將個責任塞畀你哋記者，就係因為你哋多事，所以兩個都做唔到！」及後即轉身離開，估唔到一向咁淡定嘅健釗長老咁激動！<br />\n<br />\n卓妮"},{"pid":"3cccf0507e95b09be1a8ea74f9ad07500374912f","tid":454161,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:24:11.000Z","msg":"個賊禿食得咁偏"},{"pid":"5ccd3452b27a24b498825ae3a9087dc4304f011f","tid":454161,"uid":64009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:24:11.000Z","msg":"我佛你<br />\n有何不妥？"},{"pid":"33be77847f41e0fc6027dce2e0a915a539032f0f","tid":454161,"uid":58811,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:27:54.000Z","msg":"佛門警訊創辦人翁靜晶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272ad6d6d6bcd4e8f0d727d26e20eff50bc722ff","tid":454161,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:28:36.000Z","msg":"傳教士有傳教士式<br />\n長老同尼姑用乜野式？"},{"pid":"6d604e06f0491d5e3df88a5bedb7461d76227824","tid":454161,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:29:49.000Z","msg":"佛祖心中留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90040a4a8d0a5f77ac4d0c7ae4c5c3f3c6fb187a","tid":454161,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:33:11.000Z","msg":"人地去偷練玉女心經，犯法呀？"},{"pid":"d2be02c246a8b614ae82a2960521ba00146cc423","tid":454161,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傳教士有傳教士式<br />\n長老同尼姑用乜野式？</blockquote><br />\n我佛你十八式"},{"pid":"89cdf807d2b756ff293519e12ba744afada70624","tid":454161,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:34:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>傳教士有傳教士式<br />\n長老同尼姑用乜野式？</blockquote><br />\n我佛你十八式</blockquote><br />\n佛都有火"},{"pid":"bdf18c3cfee5c8cc6c5500e60d23bd3f979d1dac","tid":454161,"uid":109164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:41:32.000Z","msg":"竹門對竹門，有乜問題"},{"pid":"5229eb72889e405536f12a9526e250bcc18ca907","tid":454161,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:45:27.000Z","msg":"我彿慈悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eaefa36194e61e8f9e6e6c81e0450a55283a999","tid":454161,"uid":137999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:46:09.000Z","msg":"唔經歷下啲塵世野又點去教徒弟"},{"pid":"589d451694f3bfc02160cc188da93e0cf4a2b6a0","tid":454161,"uid":57035,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:49:58.000Z","msg":"衲dee都叫雞食狗肉啦"},{"pid":"07b11ea138f960d98c0c4f5047dc412243e6de14","tid":454161,"uid":35860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:50:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>釋健釗後台雄厚 經常到內地弘法<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1690236&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1690236%26target%3D2&d=r%2B%2FiB006GaAC7ImnPZ1Qyb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=18e14620\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1690236%26target%3D2&h=e5e3ebcd\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1690236&amp;target=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2017/11/01/301416/i_343x255_082215716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F301416%2Fi_343x255_082215716.jpg&h=40cab3c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寶蓮寺長老釋健釗與女弟子心慧法師，被揭關係「曖昧」。<br />\n<br />\n(星島日報報道)釋健釗法師，廣東中山人，現任澳門佛教總會會長，世界佛教僧伽會副會長，澳門菩提禪院住持，荃灣南天竺寺住持，寶蓮禪寺座元和尚兼都監。<br />\n<br />\n　　一九六〇年，健釗於澳門智心佛堂依智圓長老出家，六三年赴香港寶蓮禪寺依筏可大和尚受戒，及後駐錫本港，弘法事業，八七年法師在丹霞山別傳寺接本煥長老法脈，至九四年出任澳門菩提禪院住持，九六年倡議成立「澳門佛教總會」，積極推動澳門佛教的發展，增加佛教在社會上的正面影響力，翌年創辦《澳門佛教》刊物及每年於菩提禪院舉辦靜修營，藉以讓社會大眾易於接觸和了解佛教知識。<br />\n<br />\n　　健釗亦是香港佛聯會會長釋覺光弟子，後台實力雄厚，〇九年起健釗與國家宗教局官員交往密切，經常到內地弘法。寶蓮寺於早年開始舉辦的「佛你跑」，都是健釗聯同心慧法師推廣恆常運動的概念，通過接觸不同熱愛跑步人士，雙方增進了解，尤其一般人總覺得法師是高高在上，遇到有事也不敢請教。<br />\n<br />\n　　心慧法師原籍是廣東省順德人，一九六三年出生於香港。自幼在佛教家庭中長大，所以順理成章，小學、中學都在佛教學校就讀。就讀中學期間，修讀佛學專修班三年。跟隨源慧、寬如、寬如法師學經，其後研讀楞嚴經講習班兩年。八七年五月取得文學學士學位。同年六月禮上覺下能法師出家。秋期在大嶼山寶蓮禪寺，求受三壇大戒後於藏經樓，閱讀藏經三年，主管藏經樓事務和寶蓮禪寺秘書。<br />\n<br />\n　　寶蓮禪寺天壇大佛開光後二年，就隨健釗長老轉到澳門菩提禪院，服務常住，來澳後出版澳門佛教雜誌兩年，澳門佛教總會成立後，就一直擔任主編，每期以不同筆名發表文章。於香港每年經常往佛教中學為學生作專題性的佛學講座。曾應邀到澳門普濟蓮峰學校，每星期為小四至小六的學生主講佛學四年。每年澳門菩提之旅靜修營擔任講師或導師之職。代表澳門出席世界佛教論壇並發表論文。</blockquote><br />\n佛你跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0395952b4b2426ad882db66450ecd678da663ca","tid":454161,"uid":27830,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"其實食番同行都算係咁<br />\n對咗十幾廿年無感情就假"},{"pid":"9df1d060fa3328426ee63f627b64bb835e4f4833","tid":454161,"uid":35806,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/105831_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F105831_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4146b5a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6b13a4bf68f298bc14f3fe1faa380c66fc12b9b","tid":454161,"uid":73849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:04:29.000Z","msg":"佛都會動心啦"},{"pid":"b25a68221e148e7f4fc4e178a566f8c644fb0450","tid":454161,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:06:48.000Z","msg":"點解寶蓮寺喺夏威夷會有間咁嘅屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰邊好多善信？"},{"pid":"754f30854f5b05d0f22b1038a58fdf8f8e224c86","tid":454161,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:06:56.000Z","msg":"禿奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9798ec311207d2100c001343e42fb07b6fcfb78","tid":454161,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佛呢樣野而家已經係一門生意<br />\n真係當佢清靜地就輸了</blockquote><br />\n所有宗教都係生意 仲唔洗交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n現在支那式佛教<br />\n只係掛釋達多為名"},{"pid":"621949b2620696b8857cd7f8876bb4c3a5d4dd3c","tid":454161,"uid":18349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"返到香港又大把人捐香油錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407403b95f0da62ea8b7a3e4f36e3a847fc29c89","tid":454161,"uid":88269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:15:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f032d6026dadf428ac41e61b305935857ff14b44","tid":454161,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解寶蓮寺喺夏威夷會有間咁嘅屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰邊好多善信？</blockquote><br />\n寶蓮寺有投資部門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos